<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
      <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">Welcome to GardenBook, <%= @user.name %>!</h1>

      <p>We're thrilled to have you join our community of gardening enthusiasts!</p>

      <p>GardenBook is your space to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Share your gardening journey and plant photos</li>
        <li>Connect with fellow gardeners</li>
        <li>Get tips and inspiration from the community</li>
        <li>Document your garden's growth over time</li>
      </ul>

      <p>Ready to get started?</p>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <%= link_to "Visit GardenBook", @url, style: "background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;" %>
      </p>

      <p>Happy gardening!</p>
      <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
        The GardenBook Team
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
